winning_structure.name: UBX-RXM-PMREQ-CMD
winning_structure.description: This message requests a power management related task of the receiver.

fields.name: duration
fields.description: Duration of the requested task. The maximum supported value is 12 days. Set to 0 to wait for a wakeup signal on a pin

bits.name: backup
bits.description: Set to 1 to put the receiver into backup mode

bits.name: force
bits.description: Set to 1 for minimum power consumption

fields.name: wakeupSources
fields.description: Configure pins to wake up the receiver. The receiver wakes up if there is either a falling or a rising edge on one of the configured pins.

bits.name: uartrx
bits.description: Wake up the receiver if there is an edge on the UART RX pin

bits.name: extint0
bits.description: Wake up the receiver if there is an edge on the EXTINTO pin

bits.name: extint1
bits.description: Wake up the receiver if there is an edge on the EXTINT1 pin

structure.name: UBX-RXM-PMREQ-CMD
structure.description: This message requests a power management related task of the receiver.

fields.name: duration
fields.description: Duration of the requested task. The maximum supported value is 12 days. Set to 0 to wait for a wakeup signal on a pin

bits.name: backup
bits.description: The receiver goes into backup mode for a time period defined by duration, provided that it is not connected to USB

bits.name: force
bits.description: Force receiver backup while USB is connected. USB interface will be disabled.
